text: Elina Risku (born 7 March 1992) is a Finnish speed skater. She competed in the women's 500 metres at the 2018 Winter Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish female speed skaters Category:Olympic speed skaters of Finland Category:Speed skaters at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:People from Seinäjoki
